    "arabic": "وَّ  اَبۡصِرۡ  فَسَوۡفَ یُبۡصِرُوۡنَ ﴿۱۷۹﴾ ",
    "ayat_id": 4003,
    "surah_id": 37,
    "surah_name": "As-Saaffat",
    "para_id": 23,
    "para_name": "Wa Mali"
  },
  {
